{"tid":1071603,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 比較各地飲食傳統健康程度","createTime":"2019-03-21T12:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T11:49:40.000Z","uid":56561,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8c27ebfe8f67718d20034944404e473f601836","tid":1071603,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n茶記碟頭飯下下都一大勺飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一碟牛河成千卡<br />\n一碟排骨炒麵甚至去到 1500卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都有健康選擇: 牛腩米粉加碟菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利<br />\npizza 超高卡路里<br />\n意粉高 GI<br />\n<br />\n英國<br />\n喺倫敦求其食個早餐都一大堆薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nafternoon tea 甜點高糖，鬆餅高脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國<br />\n唔洗講，睇下佢哋 obesity 比率幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中東/南亞<br />\n飛餅配肉，啖啖碳水啖啖肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有土耳其 kebab <br />\n<br />\n日本<br />\n食壽司食幾多自己話事<br />\n刺身食唔肥人<br />\n拉麵易有飽足感<br />\n<br />\n韓國<br />\n除咗烤肉，其他睇落幾健康<br />\n餐前小食有泡菜、芽菜、豆苗，碗飯又唔算多"},{"pid":"edb09ccda9d105ebb0d585de3058b4f0976f6633","tid":1071603,"uid":57984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泡菜呢啲已經唔健康啦<br />\n雖然佢都叫做係蔬菜<br />\n但係都用好多野去醃製 好高鈉"},{"pid":"1b7283a7f169e01d9874cc856380ce241a67c832","tid":1071603,"uid":18117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edb09ccda9d105ebb0d585de3058b4f0976f6633","tid":1071603,"uid":57984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泡菜呢啲已經唔健康啦<br />\n雖然佢都叫做係蔬菜<br />\n但係都用好多野去醃